<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000985/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Practices evaluation (100%):
degree of acquered knowledge on the used equipment and systems
degree of achievement of the practices specifications
Novelty, if any, over the required specifications
Evaluation will assess if students have acquired all the competences of the subject. Thus, evaluation through final assessment will be carried out considering all the evaluation techniques used in continuous evaluation (EX, ET, TG, etc.), and will be celebrated in the exam period approved by Junta de Escuela for the current academic semester and year. Evaluation activities that assess learning outcomes that cannot be evaluated through a single exam can be carried out along the semester.

Extraordinary examination will be carried out exclusively by the final examination method."""@es .

